Wallet Management Module – Non-Custodial MetaMask Integration
Arbitrage Flash Loan Platform
1. Objective
Develop a secure, non-custodial Wallet Management Module that integrates with MetaMask and serves as the central interface for wallet administration, profit distribution, and transaction monitoring within the Arbitrage Flash Loan Platform.
The platform shall never store or manage MetaMask private keys. Wallet authentication and transaction signing shall be performed through MetaMask.
2. Wallet Management Dashboard
The Wallet Management Dashboard shall display a fully sortable, searchable, and filterable table.
Wallet Management Table
Column⇅ No.⇅ Account ID⇅ Wallet Name⇅ Wallet Address⇅ Wallet Type⇅ Chain⇅ Balance⇅ Profit Balance⇅ Connection Status⇅ Active (ON/OFF Toggle)⇅ Last SynchronizationActions (Edit • Save • Delete) 
3. Table Functions
The table shall support:
Ascending / Descending sorting on every column
Multi-column sorting
Search by Account ID, Wallet Name, or Wallet Address
Filter by Blockchain
Filter by Wallet Type
Filter by Connection Status
Filter by Active/Inactive status
Column resizing
Drag-and-drop column ordering
Show/Hide columns
Sticky table header
Frozen first and last columns
Pagination (25 / 50 / 100 / 500 rows)
Row selection with checkboxes
Bulk operations
Real-time balance synchronization
