[7/5/2026 10:23 AM] Temam: 11. Security Requirements
The Wallet Management Module shall:
Operate as a non-custodial system for MetaMask wallets.
Never store, display, or manage MetaMask private keys.
Authenticate users through MetaMask.
Sign transactions through MetaMask.
Maintain complete audit logs for wallet administration activities.
Restrict administrative functions through role-based access controls.
12. Performance Requirements
The module shall:
Refresh wallet balances in real time or on demand.
Support management of hundreds to thousands of wallets.
Provide fast search, sorting, and filtering.
Maintain responsive performance during concurrent arbitrage operations.
13. Deliverables
The completed Wallet Management Module shall provide:
Non-custodial MetaMask integration
Sortable wallet management dashboard
Automatic wallet detection
Manual wallet registration
Wallet activation/deactivation
Multi-chain wallet support
Profit transfer management
Destination wallet selection
Automatic wallet rotation
Transfer history register
Export functionality (CSV, Excel, PDF)
Real-time wallet balance synchronization
Dashboard notifications
Comprehensive audit trail
